<Skein rootNode="node-1">
  <generator>Windows Inform 10.1.2</generator>
  <item nodeId="node-1">
    <command xml:space="preserve">SilentCargo</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">Helios Systems - Recovery Assignment&#x000A;&#x000A;Vessel ID: T-7366D&#x000A;&#x000A;Status: Missing&#x000A;&#x000A;Crew: Unresponsive&#x000A;&#x000A;Primary Objective: Investigate vessel and recover assigned cargo.&#x000A;&#x000A;Secondary Objective: Assess cause of communication failure.&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;No distress signal was successfully recorded.&#x000A;&#x000A;Last known position has been stabilised for boarding.&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;You are authorised to proceed.&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;The airlock cycles open with a dull, mechanical thud.&#x000A;&#x000A;Cold air spills out to meet you.&#x000A;&#x000A;Beyond it, the ship is dark.&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;No movement. No sound.&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;Just the faint hum of systems running somewhere deeper inside.&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;You step aboard.&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;--- Boarding Complete ---&#x000A;&#x000A;Airlock&#x000A;The airlock is dimly lit by a thin emergency strip. Several EVA suit lockers stand open along one wall. Most of the suits are gone. The inner hatch leads deeper into the ship.&#x000A;&#x000A;Exits: north.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-2"/>
      <child nodeId="node-13"/>
      <child nodeId="node-22"/>
      <child nodeId="node-34"/>
      <child nodeId="node-346"/>
