    <command xml:space="preserve">n</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">Medbay&#x000A;Soft white medical lights fill the bay. The diagnostic bed sits beneath a now-active terminal, its screen glowing with standby data.&#x000A;&#x000A;Exits: north, south.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
