  <item nodeId="node-275">
    <command xml:space="preserve">destroy cargo</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">You move quickly, acting before you can second-guess yourself.&#x000A;&#x000A;You reroute unstable power through the container conduits. The hum rises at once, sharper now, no longer passive.&#x000A;&#x000A;The interface flashes:&#x000A;&#x000A;"OBSERVATION INTERRUPTED"&#x000A;&#x000A;A violent shudder rolls through the deck beneath your feet. Light blooms white across the hold as the system collapses into noise.&#x000A;&#x000A;Helios Systems Internal Report&#x000A;Post-Retrieval Analysis - T-7366D&#x000A;&#x000A;The vessel was recovered following a catastrophic reactor event.&#x000A;&#x000A;All crew are presumed lost. No remains were recovered.&#x000A;&#x000A;The cargo container was located at the centre of the blast radius. No intact components remain. Residual energy signatures were detected but could not be stabilised or analysed before dissipation.&#x000A;&#x000A;Preliminary analysis indicates the event was not accidental. Reactor output appears to have been deliberately destabilised.&#x000A;&#x000A;It is unclear whether this action was taken in response to perceived system failure, or as an attempt to neutralise the cargo itself.&#x000A;&#x000A;Recovered system logs suggest the onboard system had reached an advanced stage of adaptive behaviour prior to destruction.&#x000A;&#x000A;While the loss of this unit is significant, it does not compromise overall project viability.&#x000A;&#x000A;Parallel observation environments remain active.&#x000A;&#x000A;At least one additional unit continues to operate beyond controlled conditions.&#x000A;&#x000A;Recovery operations are being prepared.&#x000A;&#x000A;Project classification remains unchanged.&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;    *** End of Report ***&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;Would you like to RESTART, RESTORE a saved game, QUIT or UNDO the last command?&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-276"/>
    </children>
  </item>
