    <result xml:space="preserve">Crew Status Summary:&#x000A;&#x000A;All crew members show elevated stress indicators.&#x000A;Sleep efficiency below recommended levels.&#x000A;No physical abnormalities detected.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
